To Rename the table - 
    Syntax - 
    RENAME TABLE <old_table_name> TO <new_table_name>;

    Example - 
    RENAME TABLE tbl_student TO studenttable;

To Empty the table data
    Syntax - 
    TRUNCATE TABLE <table_name>;

    Example - 
    TRUNCATE TABLE tbl_student;


To Delete / Drop the table 
    Syntax - 
    DROP TABLE <existing_table_name>;

    Example - 
    DROP TABLE studenttable;

To Drop / Delete the database
    Syntax - 
    DROP DATABASE <database_name>;

    Example - 
    DROP DATABASE db_school;
